  "",
  "\"Come on.\" Peter nudged her arm. \"Law. Is it so hard to pretend you're in love with me?\"",
  "",
  "The way he said this—it made her chest hurt.",
  "He knew exactly what he was doing, and the worst part was that it was working.",
