  "Alice blinked down.",
  "Suddenly before her stood a tray table, atop which sat two shiny, waxy apples.",
  "One was blood-red, the other deep green.",
  "",
  "\"What will it be?\" asked the Weaver Girl. \"Red to go on together. Green to go on alone.\"",
  "\"He has the same choice?\"",
  "\"The very same.\"",
