  "",
  "They didn’t make it.",
  "They began kissing against the chalkboard.",
  "Charlotte gasped.",
  "Professor Grimes lifted her up by the legs; rammed her back against the wall; did something with his hands that made Charlotte’s voice go up several octaves—a single moan, running up and down the scales.",
  "",
  "Alice was frozen in place, entranced and horrified, wondering if this was a tableau she wanted to join.",
  "Charlotte moaned once more.",
  "Alice’s hand slipped, and knocked into a beaker.",
  "It did not shatter—it was too far from the edge—but it did clink against another beaker, and the sound pierced the room.",
