  "He’d surely put on this effect to amuse her, and this pleased her; it meant they were still something to one another.",
  "",
  "“Bah.”",
  "He shrugged.",
  "“Of course you went.",
  "It sounds too good in theory; you always have to know.”",
  "",
  "“You were at the citadel once.”",
  "",
  "“Oh, sure.",
  "I helped build it.",
  "I have spent countless years at Gertrude’s side, planning our expanding skyline.",
