  "",
  "But she could tell she had overestimated the strength of their bond.",
  "Gradus was fond of her only when it was amusing to be.",
  "And while she considered their time together very special, she was only a fraction of his deep time.",
  "In one thousand years he would likely only chuckle at her name.",
  "",
  "“Ah . . . well.” Gradus made the sound of a throat clearing.",
  "She thought Gradus might say something more.",
  "For a moment it really did seem like he was considering it.",
  "But it was so much less awkward not to.",
  "Goodbyes were worth the effort only when you meant to see someone again.",
