  "",
  "“But he never said.” Alice sniffled, pulling the blanket tighter around her shoulders.",
  "“I wish he'd just said.”",
  "",
  "Elspeth shook her head, smiling sadly.",
  "",
  "“Magicians,” she sighed.",
