  "",
  "Archimedes mewed in agitation.",
  "Elspeth scratched the back of his neck.",
  "“Hush, you,” she murmured.",
  "“I know what I'm doing.”",
  "",
  "A small part of Alice lit up with suspicion.",
  "Surely Elspeth wanted something.",
