  "No magician ever did things out of kindness, or they wouldn't have gotten where they were.",
  "",
  "But there was no guile on Elspeth's face.",
  "Just a sweet, open sympathy.",
  "Just kindness.",
  "",
  "“But I don't deserve this.” She deserved none of the favors she had received.",
  "Peter's sacrifice, Gradus's sacrifice, now Elspeth.",
