  "“You're not searching anymore.”",
  "",
  "“I've held off the inevitable for so long.” Elspeth had a faraway look in her eyes.",
  "“And I don't want to put it off any longer.",
  "I'm tired of the Neurath, understand?",
  "I'm tired of always bobbing out at sea.",
