  "“Exactly like all the stories promised.",
  "They let you board.",
  "They let you drink.",
  "And then they take you over the horizon, to whatever lies beyond.”",
  "",
  "Elspeth rapped her knuckles against her wooden seat.",
  "“Then let's hope they'll come for me eventually.”",
  "",
  "“You're way ahead of everyone in Dis,” said Alice.",
  "“You'll do fine.”",
  "",
  "Elspeth nodded.",
  "Alice saw her lips tighten with something—fear, perhaps—but they just as soon gave way to Elspeth's typical resolve.",
  "“Any chance you could tell me how to get out of there quick?”",
  "",
  "“You think I know?”",
  "",
  "Elspeth chuckled.",
  "“Fair, that.",
