  "",
  "Oh, but it didn't matter.",
  "The academy didn't matter.",
  "Perhaps they could revise their dissertation topics in time and change their committees and scrape their way into a job, or perhaps they couldn't, but none of it mattered because the future still lay before them, delightfully open.",
